title: The yields and cross sections of delayed neutron formations at photofission of heavy elements.

x4freetext: The yields and cross sections of delayed neutron
formations at photofission of heavy elements.

x4codes.hlp: Inst. Yadernyh Doslidzhen, N.A.N.Ukraini, Kyiv, Ukraine

x4codes.shortRef: Rept: Inst. Yad. Issledovanii, Kiev Reports, No.86-36 (1986)
Rept: Inst. Yad. Issledovanii, Kiev Reports, No.82-9 (1982)
Conf: 6.All-Union Conf.on Neutron Physics,Kiev,2-6 Oct.1983, Vol.2, p.275 (1983)

x4codes.hlp: Inst. Yadernyh Doslidzhen, N.A.N.Ukraini, Kyiv, Ukraine

x4freetext: The yields and cross sections of delayed-neutron
formations are determined for the fission of Th232,
U235, U238, Np237, and Pu239 by bremsstrahlung
gamma-quanta in the range of the Ei giant resonance.
The resulting data are explained by the systematics
of the complete and absolute delayed-neutron yields
and by the five-Gauss fission products mass
Corrected by V.Varlamov: the HISTORY line
Corrected by SD and VV: REACTION code
